metadata.title: Dell 13.3" 2-in-1 Full HD Touchscreen Flagship Laptop, Intel Core i7-6500U Processor, 8GB RAM, 256GB SSD, Backlit Keyboard, 11-hour Battery Life, Windows 10
features: 6th Generation Intel Core i7-6500U Dual-Core Processor 2.5GHz (max boost speed up to 3.10 GHz) 4MB L3 Cache, Intel HD Graphics 520
13.3-inch FHD (1920 x 1080) Truelife LED-Backlit Touch Display with Wide Viewing Angle (IPS), Aspect Ratio 16:9; HD Webcam, HDMI, Bluetooth
8GB DDR3L SDRAM 1600MHz (8GBx1) memory, 256GB Solid State Hard Drive; No Optical Drive
Backlit Keyboard, Intel Dual Band Wireless AC 3165, Stereo speakers, MaxxAudio; 1xMedia Card Reader, 2xUSB 3.0, 1xUSB 2.0
Windows 10 home 64-bit, Battery life up to 11 hours. Weight: 3.66lbs; Color Silver
description: Key Features and Benefits: Signature Edition PCs, No Junkware or 3rd party trialware, The best computer meticulously configured Brilliant Full HD TrueLife display, vivid graphics and lifelike video, perfect for gaming, watching movies, and viewing photos Slim and light, With a frame that's just 0.75 inches thin and low weight of 3.4 pounds, the Inspiron 13 is a breeze to carry in a bag or tucked under your arm. Powerful Intel Core i7 processor, Faster than ever, the 6th Gen Intel Core i7 delivers striking visuals, extended battery life, and higher data transfer rates. Built to last, survive short-term heat conditions up to 149 F Display: 13.3 inch Full HD LED touchscreen (1920 x 1080), 10 finger multitouch support Processor: Intel Core i7 6500U 2.50 with Turbo Boost Technology up to 3.10 GHz Memory: 8GB DDR3 1600 MHz Hard drive size: 256GB SSD HD Operating system: Windows 10 Home, 64 bit PC type: 2-in-1 Touchscreen Convertible Stylus: Includes stylus with integrated holder Media Card Reader: SD card reader Audio: Waves MaxxAudio Pro Video: Intel HD Graphics 520 with shared graphics memory Bluetooth: Bluetooth 4.0 Wireless: 802.11ac/a/b/g/n (Miracast enabled) Keyboard, Touchpad: Backlit keyboard, Precision touchpad Ports: 3 USB 3.0 (1 PowerShare), HDMI, Headphone output/Microphone input combo WebCam: Integrated webcam Battery: 3 cell 43WHr lithium-ion Dimensions: 13.00 x 8.74 x 0.75 inch (330.00 x 222.00 x 19.00 mm) Weight: 3.44 lbs (1.56 killogram) Color: Silver
